  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "In line with the preregistered data exclusion criteria, we excluded all responses not adhering to the instruction.",
    "The remaining responses were coded as \"1\" if ChatGPT correctly identified the more acceptable sentence in the pair, and \"0\" otherwise.",
    "The first suite of statistical analyses aimed to discern the degree to which ChatGPT's grammatical intuition mirrored that of laypeople.",
    "We merged the data obtained from ChatGPT with human data from the FC task in Sprouse et al. (2013).",
    "Responses in the human dataset were re-coded as \"1\" or \"0\", akin to the ChatGPT data."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "We merged the data obtained from ChatGPT with human data from the FC task in Sprouse et al. (2013)."
  ]
}